@host = http://localhost:5056

### Health check (shows whether the API key is configured)
GET {{host}}/health

### Submit a try-on with image URLs (async). Copy the returned id.
POST {{host}}/api/vto
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "The person of image 1, maintaining exactly their face and pose, wearing the white t-shirt of image 2.",
  "person": "https://example.com/person.png",
  "garment": "https://example.com/garment.png",
  "outputFormat": "webp"
}

### Poll the job by id
GET {{host}}/api/vto/REPLACE_WITH_TASK_ID

### Submit and wait synchronously for the result image URL
POST {{host}}/api/vto/try-on
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "The person of image 1, maintaining exactly their face and pose, wearing the garments of image 2.",
  "person": "https://example.com/person.png",
  "garment": "https://example.com/garment.png",
  "outputFormat": "png"
}
